Uses of Class
com.mhealthatlas.apps.model.AndroidAppVersion

Packages that use AndroidAppVersion 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the application service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering application information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the application information state.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.helper
com.mhealthatlas.apps.helper is a group of static utility methods to convert the entity object to the dto representation.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.model
com.mhealthatlas.apps.model contains all entities form the application service database and the enum declarations.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.query
com.mhealthatlas.apps.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository
com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository contains all repository interfaces of the application service.
